WEBVTT

00:02:57.167 --> 00:03:00.393
I was going to be in a classroom
with a man every day,

00:03:00.417 --> 00:03:02.875
for a year of school.

00:03:04.208 --> 00:03:07.000
I was scared; I didn't trust him.

00:03:08.125 --> 00:03:09.393
But you know what,

00:03:09.417 --> 00:03:12.375
Mr. Randolph would turn out
to be my greatest advocate.

00:03:13.375 --> 00:03:15.143
But in the beginning,

00:03:15.167 --> 00:03:18.893
oh, I made sure he knew
I did not like him.

00:03:18.917 --> 00:03:21.268
I was noncompliant;

00:03:21.292 --> 00:03:24.875
I was that kid that was disengaged.

00:03:25.750 --> 00:03:30.143
And I also made it really hard
on my parents, too.